\,{\rm mod}\,\ p\!:\,\, 
\, {\rm ord}_p(10) = n\,
\, 10^k\equiv 1\iff n\mid k.\,
\color{#c00}{10^n\equiv 1\equiv 10^k}\Rightarrow 10^{(n,k)}\!\equiv1\,
\,(n,k) = ni+kj\ 
\,10^{(n,k)}\! = 10^{\,ni+kj}\! = (\color{#c00}{10^n})^i (\color{#c00}{10^k})^j \equiv \color{#c00}1^i \color{#c00}1^j \equiv 1.
